              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīraghuvaṃśemāhākāvye śrīkavikālidāsakṛtau dignijayonāmacaturthasargaḥ samāptaḥ śrīsāṃvasadāśivārpaṇamstumini āścinavadha 13 saumyavārasamāpto 'yaṃ // (f. 9v).</colophon>
